{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"grid","mdn_url":"/pl/docs/Web/CSS/grid","locale":"pl","native":"Polski","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\"><strong>CSS</strong></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Reference\"><strong>CSS Reference</strong></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">CSS Grid Layout</a></li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Guides</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basics concepts of grid layout</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Relationship_of_Grid_Layout\">Relationship to other layout methods</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">Line-based placement</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">Grid template areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Layout_using_Named_Grid_Lines\">Layout using named grid lines</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Auto-placement_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Auto-placement in grid layout</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Box_Alignment_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Box alignment in grid layout</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid,_Logical_Values_and_Writing_Modes\">Grids, logical values and writing modes</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Layout_and_Accessibility\">CSS Grid Layout and Accessibility</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_and_Progressive_Enhancement\">CSS Grid Layout and Progressive Enhancement</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Realizing_common_layouts_using_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Realizing common layouts using grids</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Properties</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid\">grid</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-area\">grid-area</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\">grid-auto-columns</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\">grid-auto-flow</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\">grid-auto-rows</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column\">grid-column</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-end\">grid-column-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-gap\">grid-column-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-column-start\">grid-column-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-gap\">grid-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row\">grid-row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-end\">grid-row-end</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-gap\">grid-row-gap</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-row-start\">grid-row-start</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\">grid-template</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\">grid-template-areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\">grid-template-columns</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\">grid-template-rows</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n <li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Glossary</strong></a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_lines\">Grid lines</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_tracks\">Grid tracks</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_cell\">Grid cell</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_areas\">Grid areas</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\">Gutters</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_rows\">Grid row</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_column\">Grid column</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p class=\"syntaxbox\"><strong><code>grid </code></strong>jest własnością skrótową, która ustawia wszystkie wyraźne oraz domniemane własności grid przy pomocy pojedynczej deklaracji.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"390\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/grid.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><strong>Uwaga:</strong> Można ustawić jedynie sprecyzowane bądź domniemane wartości w jednej deklaracji własności <code>grid</code>. Podwłasności, których nie określisz zostaną ustawione na wartości początkowe. Własności odstępów nie zostaną zresetowane przez ten zapis skrótowy.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"własności_składowe","title":"Własności składowe","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Ta własność jest zapisem skrótowym następujących własności</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-flow (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-areas (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-columns (en-US)</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-rows (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css no-line-numbers notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;'grid-template'&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> 100px <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span> 1fr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> [linename1] <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> 100px [linename2]<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> 200px <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span> min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"a\"</span> <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"b\"</span> 20%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 100px / 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>400px<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> min-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>auto-fill<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> 50px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;'grid-template-rows'&gt; /\n   [ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-columns'&gt;? values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 200px / auto-flow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 30% / auto-flow dense<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> [line1 line2 line3] 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / auto-flow 300px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> [line1] <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>20em<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> / auto-flow dense 40%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* [ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-rows'&gt;? /\n   &lt;'grid-template-columns'&gt; values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow / 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow dense / 30%<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow 300px / <span class=\"token function\">repeat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> [line1 line2 line3] 200px<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> auto-flow dense 40% / [line1] <span class=\"token function\">minmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>20em<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max-content<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* Global values */</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> inherit<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> initial<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> unset<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wartości","title":"Wartości","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"grid-template\"><code>&lt;'grid-template'&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd>Definiuje szablon siatki strony - własności <code>grid-template-columns</code>, <code>grid-template-rows</code> oraz <code>grid-template-areas</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"grid-template-rows_auto-flow_dense_grid-auto-columns\"><code>&lt;'grid-template-rows'&gt; / [ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-columns'&gt;?</code></dt>\n <dd>Ustawia auto-wyrównanie przy pomocy jawnych wierszy ustawionych własnością <code>grid-template-rows</code>, ustawieniem wartości <code>grid-template-rows</code> na <code>none</code> oraz określeniem w jaki sposób wykonywać automatyczne powtarzanie kolumn przy pomocy <code>grid-auto-columns</code> i ustawienie wartości <code>grid-auto-rows</code> na <code>auto</code>. <code>grid-auto-flow </code>zostaje ustawione na <code>column</code>, jeśli <code>dense</code> jest określone. Wszystkie inne podwłasności <code>grid </code>są ustawiane na wartości początkowe.</dd>\n <dt id=\"_auto-flow_dense_grid-auto-rows_grid-template-columns\"><code>[ auto-flow &amp;&amp; dense? ] &lt;'grid-auto-rows'&gt;? / &lt;'grid-template-columns'&gt;</code></dt>\n <dd>Ustawia auto-wyrównanie przy pomocy jawnych kolumn ustawionych własnością <code>grid-template-columns</code>, ustawieniem wartości własności <code>grid-template-rows </code>na <code>none </code>oraz określeniem w jaki sposób wykonywać automatyczne powtarzanie wierszy przy pomocy <code>grid-auto-rows </code>i ustawienie wartości <code>grid-auto-columns </code>na <code>auto</code>.<code> grid-auto-flow </code>zostaje ustawione na <code>row</code>, jeśli <code>dense</code> jest określon. Wszystkie inne podwłasności <code>grid </code>są ustawiane na wartości początkowe.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"formalna_definicja","title":"Formalna definicja","isH3":false,"content":"<p><table class=\"properties\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/CSS/initial_value\">Wartość początkowa</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-rows (en-US)</a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-columns (en-US)</a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-areas (en-US)</a>: <code>none</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: <code>auto</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: <code>auto</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-flow (en-US)</a>: <code>row</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>0</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">column-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>normal</code></li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row-gap (en-US)</a>: <code>normal</code></li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Stosowana do</th><td>grid containers</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\">Dziedziczona</a></th><td>no</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Percentages</th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-rows (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-columns (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: refer to corresponding dimension of the content area</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/CSS/warto%c5%9b%c4%87_wyliczona\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Wartość wyliczona</a></th><td>as each of the properties of the shorthand:<br><ul><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-rows (en-US)</a>: as specified, but with relative lengths converted into absolute lengths</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-columns (en-US)</a>: as specified, but with relative lengths converted into absolute lengths</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-areas\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-template-areas (en-US)</a>: jako określone</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-rows (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-columns (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-flow\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-auto-flow (en-US)</a>: jako określone</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-column-gap (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">grid-row-gap (en-US)</a>: the percentage as specified or the absolute length</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/column-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">column-gap (en-US)</a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/row-gap\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">row-gap (en-US)</a>: as specified, with &lt;length&gt;s made absolute, and normal computing to zero except on multi-column elements</li></ul></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Animation type</th><td>discrete</td></tr></tbody></table></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"formalna_składna","title":"Formalna składna","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-template'&gt; (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-rows\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-template-rows'&gt; (en-US)</a> / <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">[ (en-US)</a> auto-flow <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#double_ampersand\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&amp;&amp; (en-US)</a> dense<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">] (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-auto-columns'&gt; (en-US)</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#single_bar\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">| (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">[ (en-US)</a> auto-flow <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#double_ampersand\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&amp;&amp; (en-US)</a> dense<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#brackets\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">] (en-US)</a> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-rows\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-auto-rows'&gt; (en-US)</a><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Value_definition_syntax#question_mark\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">? (en-US)</a> / <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;'grid-template-columns'&gt; (en-US)</a></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykłady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"tworzenie_układu_grid_układ_siatki","title":"Tworzenie układu grid (układ siatki)","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>c